* Dedicated Group Access Mode
** Assigns compute to single user/group
** Permission scoping
***_ User's permissions reduce to group's
***_ Prevents privilege escalation
***_ Enables secure group collaboration
** Supports
***_ Databricks Runtime ML
***_ RDD APIs
***_ R language
** Requirements
***_ Unity Catalog enabled
***_ Databricks Runtime 15.4+
***_ Group needs CAN MANAGE on workspace folder
** Data object ownership
***_ Objects owned by group, not individual
***_ e.g. CREATE SCHEMA owned by group
** Setup
*** Create compute
****_ Access mode: Dedicated
***_ Assign group in "Single user or group"
*** Create group folder
****_ /Workspace/Groups/<groupName>
****_ Grant CAN MANAGE to group
@endmindmap
